# Generated images: hero images are produced locally and must be committed so
# the production deploy includes them (CF serves /public/* from the bundle).
# To regenerate the entire set: `python3 scripts/backfill_images.py` (slow,
# VexoAPI editimg ~70s per image). Individual images: `python3 scripts/gen_recipe_image.py --slug X --title Y`.
# public/images/recipes/*.png
# public/images/recipes/*.jpg

